==Introduction==
Hello everyone, this is Death Usagi.

This is a newly revised Guide that will help you power level your beloved Destroyers (DD) and Light Cruisers (CL) in World 4-3!

This guide is to give you guidance in order to help your DD/CL obtain MVP consistently in World 4-3 to level up efficiently.

Please read through this Guide thoroughly to know the strategy to have your DD/CL level up consistently throughout your runs.

==World 4-3 Map==

[[File:4-3_Map_Edit.jpg|thumb|center|600px]]

The Strategy of World 4-3 Power Leveling is to have your DD or CL Flagship that you wish to level up gain MVP in nodes F and D or K consistently.

There may be times where you are sent to node J and by 1/3 chance face the {{ShipLink|Battleship Ta-Class Flagship}} Enemy Fleet from that node, but depending on your own luck, you may get away with it, or come out with a Medium-Damaged Ship or be forced to retreat immediately due to a Ship(s) getting Heavily Damaged from the battle...

